title: Sepahan Khurouj Bushehr F.C.
text:
Sepahan Khurouj Bushehr Football Club is an Iranian <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Bushehr">Bushehr</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. They currently compete in the <a href="2011%E2%80%9312%20Hazfi%20Cup">2011–12 Hazfi Cup</a>.
